![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/585127af-ccf8-496b-98b6-a9d68258f16b/Screenshot_20240724-170357_TrillerTV.jpg)

AEW Dynamite opens with MJF coming to the ring and expressing disgust over the International title being a “_workhorse"_ championship.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/7e247e66-dfcb-48df-942d-f3308fdcab7a/Screenshot_20240724-170945_TrillerTV.jpg)

MJF throws the International Championship in the trash and rechristened the title.

This is now the AEW American Championship to represent "the best country in the world"

Confetti, patriotic music and an MJF themed American Flag rain down.

Ospreay comes out to chase MJF out of the Ring and make it official.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/a7e9091b-5810-4d40-a018-5ec5f3023de8/20240724_171734.jpg)

MJF vs Will Ospreay 2 is set for All In at Wembley Stadium!!!!

