![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/3c0f8c98-a67c-432c-b94a-9f1c045da268/20240724_173719.jpg)

*   ## **_CHRIS JERICHO DEF. MINORU SUZUKI TO RETAIN THE FTW CHAMPIONSHIP_**
    

Brutal chop battle that has Jericho's chest cut open at one point.

Post match the Learning Tree tries to attack Suzuki but Shibata comes out to save him!

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/92bd08e6-b230-4db1-b6f3-ae6914efaf44/20240724_173703.jpg)

Kris Statlander attacked Willow Nightingale backstage and asks for a shot at the CMLL Women's World Championship

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/9cb9cb70-f73d-4cc3-8831-3ae223c530b5/20240724_174432.jpg)

Jeff Jarrett tells Bryan Danielson that he was the perfect guy to win the Owen but he needs to lock in and not let Swerve into his head.

