![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/ff13b6f1-521f-40fa-b5a9-fc8f1745f23f/20240724_175519.jpg)

KAMILLE HAS FINALLY ARRIVED IN AEW!!!!

*   ## **_Britt Baker def. Hikaru Shida_**
    

Post match Mercedes Moné runs out and asks Britt if she wants a title shot at Wembley? Well she can't have it.

KAMILLE ATTACKS BRITT FROM BEHIND! KAMILLE IS ALIGNED WITH MERCEDES MONE

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/d78ba62d-2fed-49c3-9ca9-2212d30f2de0/PhotoGrid_1_20240724181345.jpg)

Mariah May makes quick work of the local talent and then she's attacked by Toni Storm.

They begin to brawl before the referee's break them up.

Great segment. Maybe the best story in AEW right now.

