![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/55102116-6815-4d90-ad8c-518129c440de/20240724_182058.jpg)

*   ## **_BLOOD AND GUTS: TEAM AEW VS THE ELITE_**
    

The match is everything you want it to be violence wise.

Hangman Page is the final entrant for the Elite but he doesn't come out for his entrance.

He waits for Swerve and attacks him from behind. Chair to the back of the head and then he handcuffs Swere to the cage and beats him senseless.

The Young Bucks are screaming at Hangman because they have a deal. Hangman doesn't care.

But now the Bucks tell him if he doesn't get in the ring, he's fired. Hangman gets in the ring and confronts them but Okada pushed Hangman away.

Team AEW attacks before Hangman and Okada can fight and Blood and Guts officially begins.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/524e1fb9-a8c5-4fe1-9016-d728de81b19c/20240724_185715.jpg)

TEAM AEW DEF. THE ELITE AFTER DARBY ALLIN POURED GASOLINE ONTO A HANDCUFFED JACK PERRY AND THREATED TO LIGHT HIM AFLAME IF HE WASNT GIVEN A TNT TITLE SHOT AT ALL IN

JACK PERRY DOESN'T CARE BUT THE BUCKS DO IT FOR HIM!!!

